<div class="feature-desc">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.lamar.edu/admissions/paying-for-college/index.html">Paying for College</a></h2>
<p>A college education is an investment in your future. Learn more about financial aid and scholarships.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a aria-label="Learn more about paying for college" href="https://www.lamar.edu/admissions/paying-for-college/index.html">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="animation: pulse 2s infinite; margin-left: 5px;"></i></a></p>
