        <section><div class="rowcontainer " style="background:linear-gradient(125deg,rgba(0,0,0,0.55) 45%,rgba(176,12,20,0.7) 35%),url(https://www.lamar.edu/_files/images/centennial/centennialbg.jpg); background-position:50% 30%; background-size:cover;">
                                         <div class="row lighttxt ">
                         
                                         
                        
            
            
            

               
                                
                <div class="large-5 columns ">
                                        
                                                 
                
                                 <h2 style="text-align: center;">CELEBRATING 100 YEARS</h2>
<p><a href="centennial/index.html"><img alt="Lamar University Centennial 1923 - 2003" height="150" src="https://www.lamar.edu/_files/images/marketing-communications/centennial-marks-guidelines/logos/stand-alone/100-centennial-white.png" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="325"/></a></p>
                                     </div>
                
                                           
            
            
            

               
                                
                <div class="large-6 columns ">
                                        
                                                 
                
                                 <p><br/>An important part of Lamar University&#8217;s institutional identity is tied to the 1901 Spindletop oil gusher, which set the foundation for South Park Junior College&#8217;s creation in 1923.</p>
<p>Much like the Lucas oil gusher in 1901, LU is bursting with opportunity for a wide range of students. Join us in celebrating this moment and the rich history of Lamar University.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button black" href="centennial/index.html">LEARN MORE</a></p>
